(192, 'International Conference Public Health 2022', 'international-conference-public-health-2022', '<h3><strong>Announcement of Abstract and Poster Accepted on The 1st MICTOPH</strong></h3> <p>Here we attach the announcement of the abstract and poster accepted after going through the review process.</p> <p>We congratulate those who are accepted and thank you very much for all the participation of the registrants. See you on November 12th!</p> <p><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1l1cmvM3WtMs2hPZk6blupH71Ixspwag8/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\">Click here</a></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h4><strong>Title</strong></h4> <p>&ldquo;The First Mulawarman International Conference on Tropical Public Health&rdquo;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h4><strong>Theme</strong></h4> <p>&ldquo;Digital Health for Public Health on Post-Pandemic Covid-19&rdquo;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h4><strong>Time and The place Implementation</strong></h4> <p>This conference will be held on:</p> <p>Day, date :&nbsp;<strong>Saturday , November 12, 2022</strong></p> <p>The place :&nbsp;<strong>Online via zoom meeting</strong>&nbsp;(based on the Faculty Public Health , University Mulawarman , Samarinda , Indonesia)</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <h4><strong>SPEAKER</strong></h4> <p><img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/659281f0dfb8ba2275996368a6649aa1.jpg\" width=\"721\" height=\"152\" /><strong><br /></strong></p> <p><strong><img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/5a44b299b5441b17940a73a956a1a3fb.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"718\" height=\"404\" /></strong></p> <h4><strong>REGISTRATION</strong></h4> <p><strong>Participant</strong></p> <p>The target participants for this international conference are students (S1, S2, S3), alumnus, and professionals in the fields of health and education (target participants: 300 people). Participants will get certificates for both attending as presenters and participants after participating in conference activities.</p> <p>oral presenters and seminar participants will get certificates with SKP (employee performance goals) of professional organizations (IAKMI and PERSAKMI).</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Registration</strong></p> <p>Participants can register themselves as presenters (oral or poster) and webinar participants via link :&nbsp;<strong><a href=\"https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022</a></strong></p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Payment Virtual Account&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Payment Virtual Account : 9880460200100018</p> <p>Name : The 1st MICTOPH</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Registration Fee</strong></p> <p><strong>Registration fee for oral presenter (include seminar participation fee):</strong><br />- General : IDR 500.000<br />- Doctoral student : IDR 350.000<br />- Master student : IDR 250.000<br />- Bachelor student : IDR 100.000<br />#International Presenter: USD 35</p> <p><strong>Registration Fee for Poster (include seminar participation fee):</strong></p> <p>- General IDR 350.000<br />- Doctoral IDR 200.000<br />- Master IDR 150.000<br />- Bachelor IDR 75.000<br />- International USD 20</p> <p><strong>Seminar participant fee:</strong><br />- From FKM UNMUL: free<br />- Outside FKM UNMUL : IDR 50.000<br />#International Participant (non presenter) : USD 7</p> <p><strong>Publication Fee:</strong><br />Scopus or Web of Science index proceedings will be informed later.</p> <p><strong>Contact Person:</strong></p> <p>+6281355916627 (Nurul)<br />+6287865692030 (Rina)</p> <p>E-mail:<br />mictoph@fkm.unmul.ac.id</p> <p><strong>Call for Paper</strong></p> <p><strong>Topic :</strong>&nbsp;Digital Health for Public Health on Post-Pandemic Covid-19 (based on the 8 pillars of public health)</p> <p><strong>Sub- topics :</strong></p> <ol> <li>Biostatistics and Population</li> <li>Environmental Health</li> <li>Health Promotion</li> <li>Nutrition</li> <li>Occupational Health and Safety</li> <li>Health Administration and Policy</li> <li>Epidemiology</li> <li>Child and Maternal Health</li> </ol> <p><strong>Provision Writing Abstract</strong></p> <ol> <li>Title should not exceed 15 words</li> <li>Abstract manuscript consisting of one page with a maximum of 250 words, which is made in English</li> <li>Abstract contains background, objectives, research methods, results, suggestions, and keywords</li> <li>If non-research / community service results, the abstract can contain: background, objectives, implementation methods, results (activity stages, review results, etc.), lessons learned, and keywords.</li> <li>Abstract writing using Times New Roman font, size 12 pts and spacing 1</li> <li>Abstracts are sent in Microsoft Word format.</li> <li>Abstract sent via link :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://bit.ly/RegistrationMICTOPH2022\">Upload Your Abstract</a></li> </ol> <p><strong>Provision Presentation Video Delivery</strong></p> <ol> <li>Videos collected after the selection process of abstract announced and participant received a Letter of Acceptance ( LoA )</li> <li>Video showing presenter and presentation slides</li> <li>Video duration max 7 minutes</li> <li>Maximum video capacity 100 mb</li> <li>Videos collected on the link&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.gle/m5X7KFWEpT4dZLUr7\">Upload Your Video</a></li> </ol> <p><strong>Provision Script Complete Article (Full Paper)</strong></p> <ol> <li>Full text of a maximum of 4000 words</li> <li>Complete manuscript structure: <ol style=\"list-style-type: lower-alpha;\"> <li>Title</li> <li>Abstract and keywords</li> <li>Introduction</li> <li>Purpose</li> <li>Research method / implementation Method</li> <li>Results and Discussion</li> <li>Suggestions / lessons learned</li> </ol> </li> <li>Maximum Full Paper capacity 10&nbsp;mb</li> <li>Articles are collected on the link&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.gle/m5X7KFWEpT4dZLUr7\">Upload Your Abstract</a></li> </ol> <p><strong>Provision Poster Complete (Poster Presentation)</strong></p> <p>1. Customize the content of the poster with the template</p> <p>2. Please complete the poster with pictures and/or diagrams</p> <p>3. Upload the complete poster at the following link&nbsp;<a href=\"https://forms.gle/VHU5As61jGjJEoV16\">Upload Your&nbsp;Poster<br /><br /></a></p> <p><strong>Article Publication</strong></p> <ol> <li>Prior to the conference, participants will be given a book of abstract</li> <li>After the conference activities and complete articles have been collected, the selected articles will be published in the Web of Science or Scopus indexed proceedings.</li> </ol> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p><strong>Poster&nbsp;Template&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Download&nbsp;Poster&nbsp;Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1tyd1b09U2AzAbooc1JWi6KZdQp43QVU2/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=100104818473757789352&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p> <p><strong>Abstract Template&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Download Abstract Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/10bMiQHo3FOn7fGOqGXHGJaRe14bgqX8U/edit?usp=sharing&amp;ouid=100104818473757789352&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p> <p><strong>Full Paper Template&nbsp;</strong></p> <p>Download Full Paper Template&nbsp; here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/14DnGtMQvpLAWAdZBvK4STgTfxiMDqkWG/edit?usp=share_link&amp;ouid=107937252377523467476&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p> <p><strong>Term of Reference</strong></p> <p><strong><img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/1f84c097a8f075eaca70e3757356e9a7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"456\" height=\"1054\" /></strong></p> <p>Download Term of Reference&nbsp;here :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rOs1DB6yzi6AMBnY6uiLRqdzfooCxXnf/view?usp=share_link\" target=\"_blank\">Download</a></p> <p><strong>Co-Host</strong></p> <p><img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/2f87943bd2ea4fe455483360ef4e550c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"101\" height=\"102\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/0e6a2e03c942419b6ecc41b6e2798cea.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"108\" height=\"108\" />&nbsp;<img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/7c4e3a9b611a9a0c71af106a80f3d65c.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"103\" height=\"105\" /></p> <p><img src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/085bce8266daa1c68d4f329269424727.jpg\" width=\"724\" height=\"98\" /></p> <p>&nbsp;</p>', '5394398112fa006c5d76a2f369c15d39.JPG', 'International Seminar', 100, '2022-11-02 06:39:00', 'admin', 'Berita', '2013-09-13'),
(193, 'Selamat Bapak Dr. Ir. H. Abdunnur, M.Si Rektor Universitas Mulawarman', 'selamat-bapak-dr.-ir.-h.-abdunnur,-m.si-rektor-universitas-mulawarman', '<p>Segenap Keluarga Besar Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat mengucapkan selamat kepada Dr. Ir. h. Abdunnur, M.Si Yang telah terpilih menjadi Rektor Universitas Mulawarman. Semoga bapak selalu diberikan keberkahan dalam mengemban amanah besar ini.</p>', 'e56b17f35ec460f6b88851775418360e.jpg', 'Ucapan Selamat Kepada Rektor Terpilih', 100, '2022-10-29 03:20:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-14'),
(194, 'Terima Kasih Bapak Prof. Dr. H. Masjaya, M.Si', 'terima-kasih-bapak-prof.-dr.-h.-masjaya,-m.si', '<p>Keluarga Besar Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat mengucapkan terima kasih banyak kepada bapak Prof. Dr. H. Masjaya M.Si yang telah mendedikasikan diri sebagai Rektor Universitas Mulawarman</p>', '88e50d99b66a6f9c7ae5024e1132da93.jpg', 'Ucapan Terima Kasih kepada Rektor', 100, '2022-10-29 04:49:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-15'),
(195, 'Rincian Kebutuhan Pegawai PPPK Kebutuhan Tenaga Teknis di FKM UNMUL Tahun 2022', 'rincian-kebutuhan-pegawai-pppk-kebutuhan-tenaga-teknis-di-fkm-unmul-tahun-2022', '<p>Menindaklanjuti Pengumuman dari Kementerian Pendidikan, Kebudayaan, Riset dan Teknologi Nomor: 72057/A.A3/KP.01.01/2022 Tanggal 20 Desember 2022, tentang Seleksi Penerimaan Pegawai Pemerintah dengan Perjanjian Kerja (PPPK) Kebutuhan Tenaga Teknis Kementerian Pendidikan, Kebudayaan, Riset Dan Teknologi Tahun Anggaran 2022, maka dengan ini Dekan Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat Universitas Mulawarman membuka kesempatan kepada Warga Negara Indonesia yang memiliki integritas dan komitmen tinggi menjadi Pegawai Pemerintah dengan Perjanjian Kerja (PPPK) Kebutuhan Tenaga Teknis untuk mengisi lowongan kebutuhan Tahun Anggaran 2022. Demikian kami sampaikan,Informasi kebutuhan jabatan PPPK dapat dilihat pada laman: https://casn.kemendikbud.go.id/ . Atas perhatian dan kerjasamanya diucapkan terima kasih.</p>', '1da54eedb7badb1a5bdd3eb87a2cb193.png', 'PPPK dosen', 100, '2022-12-22 03:43:00', 'admin', 'Pengumuman', '2013-09-16'),
(198, 'PENERIMAAN MAHASISWA BARU PRODI S2 FAKULTAS KESEHATAN MASYARAKAT', 'penerimaan-mahasiswa-baru-prodi-s2-fakultas-kesehatan-masyarakat', '<p>Program Studi Magister Kesehatan Masyarakat membuka pendaftaran mahasiswa baru.<br />akan dimulainya semester ganjil tahun akademik 2023/2024 pada&nbsp;agustus&nbsp;mendatang Prodi magister Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat Universitas Mulawarman telah membuka pendaftaran untuk mahasiswa baru.<br />segera daftarkan diri anda di prodi Magister FKM Unmul.<br />berikut link brosur untuk detil informasi yang ingin anda ketahui.<br />link pendaftaran juga terdapat di dalam brosur berikut<br /><br /><a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1q75g0LZN1Uy9kfgvwFKTThXEPPi1sjkM/view?usp=share_link\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1q75g0LZN1Uy9kfgvwFKTThXEPPi1sjkM/view?usp=share_link</a><br /><br />salam sehat</p>', 'fcc158a13465a8aeec00a1e32b16e250.jpg', 'PENERIMAAN MAHASISWA BARU MAGISTER', 100, '2023-03-17 19:05:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-17'),
(199, 'Arisan Gabungan Dharma Wanita Persatuan Universitas Mulawarman Tahun 2023', 'arisan-gabungan-dharma-wanita-persatuan-universitas-mulawarman-tahun-2023', '<p>Arisan?Gabungan Dharma Wanita Persatuan Universitas Mulawarman Tahun 2023 merupakan kegiatan rutin yang di lakukan oleh dharma wanita di lingkungan Universitas Mulawarman<br />dalam rangkaian yang dilakukan pada kegiatan ini panitia dharma wanita juga telah memberikan pemeriksaan kesehatan tanpa biaya, bermain game Ranking 1 dengan tema kesehatan serta diberikan penyuluhan rumah bebas asap rokok oleh salah satu dosen di Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat yakni Hj Nur Rohmah, SKM., M.Kes Ph.D.</p>', '13aa83275f0e8791688898541c3c2c96.jpg', '?Arisan GabunganDharma Wanita Persatuan Unmul dan', 100, '2023-03-17 19:38:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-18'),
(200, 'MARHABAN YA RAMADHAN', 'marhaban-ya-ramadhan', '<p>Selamat datang bulan ramadhan,<br />Mari kita semua berharap kita akan mendapatkan pahala yang sebesar besarnya pada Ramadhan kali ini.<br /><br />Tetap jaga kesehatan agar kita dapat beribadah dengan maksimal', '07f0d022190266a667fdc96739ec1a31.jpg', 'MARHABAN YA RAMADHAN', 100, '2023-03-29 15:16:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-19'),
(201, 'Chandra Pangli Lolo, Mahasiswa FKM Unmul Angkatan 2021, Juara 1 Duta Genre Kota Samarinda', 'chandra-pangli-lolo,-mahasiswa-fkm-unmul-angkatan-2021,-juara-1-duta-genre-kota-samarinda', '<p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Pimpinan Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat Universitas Mulawarman Mengucapkan Selamat Ananda Chandra Pangli Lolo, Mahasiswa Angkatan 2021 yang telah berhasil menjadi juara 1 Duta Generasi Berencana&nbsp;Kota Samarinda<br />semoga pencapaian ini dapat bermanfaat untuk orang orang di sekitar terkhususnya untuk Ananda sendiri. Serta dapat memberikan motivasi kepada teman teman mahasiswa FKM Unmul untuk semangat dalam berpartisipasi pada kegiatan serupa.</p> <p>#Genre #FKMUNMUL #KESMASUNMUL #UNMUL #universitasmulawarman</p>', '31c901ccbd9316316a67d653b375fda0.jpg', 'Apresiasi Civitas Juara 1 Duta Genre Kota Samarind', 100, '2023-06-17 23:03:00', 'RezaNurFahmi', 'Berita', '2013-09-20'),
(202, 'The Second Mulawarman International Conference on Tropical Public Health', 'the-second-mulawarman-international-conference-on-tropical-public-health', '<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/ee94a028d78c9ad85445b3ab7ddb0a64.jpg\" style=\"height:591px; width:591px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"/writable/uploads/content/galeri/490562d7921c8e0b03e91051a768fcb3.jpg\" style=\"height:591px; width:591px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dengan penuh kebanggaan, kami mengucapkan Alhamdulillah atas terselenggaranya The Second Mulawarman International Conference on Tropical Public Health. Kami Mengucapkan terima kasih yang sebesar besarnya kepada seluruh elemen yang telah berpartisipasi dalam kegiatan ini, semoga Keberkahan selalu tercurahkan kepada seluruh pihak yang telah berkontribusi dalam suksesnya seminar Internasional Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat. Sampai berjumpa di Seminar Internasional Fakultas Kesehatan Masyarakat di Tahun ke Tiga InsyaAllah</p>\r\n', '8f29262136bd9f2b4b88e82db0edf630.jpg', 'The Second Mulawarman International Conference on', 100, '2023-10-06 08:35:00', 'ajisudjay', 'Berita', '2013-09-21');
